  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Game Guide\n\nCore\nThe game is split into two core gameplay modes. Exploration
    and Combat. You win the game by achiving victory points! These points are gained
    when you \"Clear\" a special node! (The purple nodes). Clearing in this case
    means, supplying them with enough resources to clear them from the exploration
    map!\n\nYour base at the center of the exploration map, will be the target of
    hostile drones! You can spawn defensive tower nodes to help protect your home
    base and fight them manually!\n\nSpecial and Tower are two types of \"Nodes\"
    out of four! The rest are resource and hazzard nodes! Hazzard nodes block areas
    from being traversed and needs to be cleared like how special nodes can! Resource
    nodes are the basic way to get resources!\n\nYou also get resources when manually
    fighting hostiles! Hostiels defeated by towers will not give resources! \n\nYou
    use \"Caravans\" to both take and supply resources! When you move with your \"Explorer
    drone\" towards a node, a UI pop up will appear! Intereact to spawn a caravan
    towards it! (Towers need resources to fire, so you also need to send caravans
    to them!)"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
